# Example CLAUDE.local.md - Personal Workflow Configuration

This is an example of what you can include in your personal CLAUDE.local.md file.
Copy this to CLAUDE.local.md and customize it for your workflow.

## Personal MCP Configuration

```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "amux": {
      "command": "/path/to/your/amux/bin/amux",
      "args": ["mcp", "--git-root", "/path/to/your/project"],
      "env": {}
    }
  }
}
```

## Your Workflow Preferences

### When Working on Issues

- Always create descriptive workspace names
- Document progress in context files
- Run tests before committing

### Personal Aliases or Commands

```bash
# Your custom aliases
alias amux-clean='amux ws prune --days 3'
alias amux-status='amux ws list && git status'
```

